				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$F_{C0}^{\left( {sc} \right)} \left( t \right) = F_{C0} \left( t \right)\frac{{P_{C12} \left( {14\,{\rm hr}} \right)}}{{P_{C0} \left( {14\,{\rm hr}} \right)}}$$\end{document}
We found that the shape of the loading/unloading curve was similar whether CytoD was added before or after initiation of cyclic stretch. We then subtracted this scaled, or normalized, force curve from the force curve for the ring with CytoD added after 12 h to obtain an estimated cell force (Fig. 3):
2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
